01:54:38.800 --> 01:54:43.795
It was rough, but it was a blessing. Back then, we thanked God for it.

01:54:43.796 --> 01:54:49.205
I don't ever condemn anybody because I was there for years, and it was like God helped me being a janitor.

01:54:49.206 --> 01:54:56.202
We lived by paychecks and we didn't even have it. We were so thankful for those food stamps.

01:54:56.203 --> 01:55:03.451
I don't ever sit here and beat on anybody's head because I lived it for more than 10 years, and God provided, and we are thankful.

01:55:03.452 --> 01:55:15.792
I know what it's like to not have that on the first and think, 'Oh my gosh.'So I'm never going to poke anybody. I know exactly.

01:55:15.793 --> 01:55:24.079
There's always going to be people in every situation that abuse stuff, but there are people that rightfully need that help.

01:55:24.080 --> 01:55:27.626
Yeah, because I was there. Thank God. It bought our meat. It bought our bread.

01:55:27.627 --> 01:55:32.333
It bought our peanut butter. It bought everything we needed for that month.

01:55:32.334 --> 01:55:36.165
The church didn't pay us much, but we made it and God provided.

01:55:36.166 --> 01:55:44.220
We made it through. So we don't want the people to go without on the first. I can't imagine what we would have done back then.

01:55:44.221 --> 01:55:54.686
If they say, 'Well, are you going to have it?'we would have to go out and get another job and do more and more work even making what we had.

01:55:54.687 --> 01:56:01.470
Thank God for it. It's pride. You know, a lot of times as a man, you don't want to have to do that.

01:56:01.471 --> 01:56:06.128
You think, 'Oh God, you've been a lousy husband or a lousy father.'It was not that.

01:56:06.129 --> 01:56:13.255
I worked my tail end off; I just didn't have an education at the time.

01:56:13.256 --> 01:56:20.759
God has been faithful to Brandon. So we love you all and we want to thank you for joining us tonight.

01:56:20.760 --> 01:56:27.799
Paisley wants to say hi. 'Hi, everybody. Hi, everybody.'She's a good kid.

01:56:27.800 --> 01:56:42.580
One day I'll let you on here, but not now. Do they have any questions?

01:56:42.581 --> 01:56:53.559
That's it. Nope. Well, we love you. Remember, thank you for praying for us and praying with us.

01:56:53.560 --> 01:56:56.534
Yes. Remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

01:56:56.535 --> 01:56:59.809
We'll see you again tomorrow. We'll keep praying. I felt I should keep praying.

01:56:59.810 --> 01:57:14.699
It's been interesting because it's been about the October 31st praying, every day really trying to hit this hard to get this government back open and get this budget passed so we don't have craziness because I've already told you the result of it.

01:57:14.700 --> 01:57:20.471
But I already know God has a plan, and we're going to stop this in the name of Jesus.

01:57:20.472 --> 01:57:26.879
And we're not going to allow our nation to get burned up and get craziness.

01:57:26.880 --> 01:57:31.977
We're going to believe God for revival. But remember, put a smile on your face, song in your heart.

01:57:31.978 --> 01:57:39.990
Jesus loves you so much and we love you. God bless you and we'll see you again soon.

